OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAfghanistan's female TV    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpresenters must cover their
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ffaces, say Taliban         
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Taliban have ordered female Afghan 
OL,6, TV presenters and other women on screen
OL,7, to cover their faces while on air.     
OL,9,FMedia outlets were told of the decree  
OL,10,Fon Wednesday, a religious police       
OL,11,Fspokesman told BBC Pashto.             
OL,13,FThe ruling comes two weeks after all   
OL,14,Fwomen were ordered to wear a face veil 
OL,15,Fin public, or risk punishment.         
OL,17,FRestrictions are being tightened on    
OL,18,Fwomen - they are banned from travelling
OL,19,Fwithout a male guardian and secondary  
OL,20,Fschools are shut for girls.            
